      "author": "SirwanAfifi",
      "description": "Inkplane 0.2.0 introduces the Pencil-first infinite canvas experience for Obsidian.\n\n## Highlights\n\n- Dedicated `.inklayer` drawing files with full-canvas editing and note embeds\n- Improved Apple Pencil rendering, pressure handling, palm rejection, pan, and zoom\n- Pen, highlighter, eraser, lasso, undo/redo, and SVG export tools\n- Area erasing and a refreshed compact toolbar\n- Mobile-safe Obsidian APIs with no telemetry or network requests\n\nInstall with BRAT from `https://github.com/SirwanAfifi/inkplane`, or download `main.js`, `manifest.json`, and `styles.css` below for manual installation.\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/SirwanAfifi/inkplane/compare/0.1.0...0.2.0",
